Description: User visits homepage of iCommons Webapp.

User opens a web browser and navigates to http://rack113.cs.drexel.edu/

User is presented with a functional homepage for the iCommons App
CCI logo caption is present on the page.
A list of occupied rooms are displayed on the page.
A list of available rooms are displayed on the page.
User is allowed to scroll when viewing the list of occupied rooms.
Middle section of the page consists of a CCI photo and caption that the Administrator changes.
Site footer is displayed at the bottom of the screen.
Advanced Search button is located at the bottom of the screen.
User is able to view background image.
User waits for page to load
Upon clicking the CCI logo, the user is redirected to Drexel’s website.
User clicks on CCI logo in the top left corner of the page.
User is redirected to Drexel’s website.
Upon clicking the Reserve Room link on the toolbar, the user the user is redirected to a page to reserve a conference room.
User clicks the Resource Reservation option.
User clicks on the Reserve Room link.
User is redirected to a page to reserve a conference room.
